    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For me</p>\n<pre><code>object Hello {\n   const val MAX_LEN = 20\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>was to much boilerplate. I simple put the static final fields above my class like this</p>\n<pre><code>private val MIN_LENGTH = 10 // &lt;-- The `private` scopes this variable to this file. Any class in the file has access to it.\n\nclass MyService{\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
