  "title" : "What is the equivalent of Java static final fields in Kotlin?",
  "body" : "<p>In Java, to declare a constant, you do something like:</p>\n<pre><code>class Hello {\n    public static final int MAX_LEN = 20;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>What is the equivalent in Kotlin?</p>\n"
